posting_body: ['Check out our YouTube Page at <URL> to see all Prescott Wallingford has to Offer!', 'Welcome Home to Prescott Wallingford!', 'Two bedrooms- two baths with den', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 54', 'OR Text', '54', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1034 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Controlled Access Doors', '- Full-Size In-Unit Washer and Dryer', '- 17-Foot Ceilings*', '- Walk-in Closets*', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Vaulted Ceilings*', '- Decks, patios, or private rooftop terraces*', '- Vinyl Floors*', '- Versatile Track Lighting Systems', '*Select units only.', 'Community Amenities', '- On-Site Storage Units', '- Pea Patch Garden Bins', '- Lease Terms from 3-13 months', '- 3 On-Site BBQ Grills', '- Package Lockers', '- Gated Access Parking Garage', '- Easy Access to I-5, 99 & Bus Route 62/26', '- FOB Access Doors', '- Community Lounge w/ Wi-fi', '- Fitness center', '- Night Patrol', '- Roof -Top w/ Spectacular Views', '- Off-Leash Dog Run', '- Conference Room w/ Wi-fi', '- On-Site Bike Storage', 'Pet Policy', 'Our apartments accommodate up to two pets per home.', 'Additional deposits and breed restrictions apply.', 'Income Requirements:', 'Income must be 3 times the amount of rent to qualify.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Prescott Wallingford', '3920 Stone Way North, Seattle, WA, 98103', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'YgMQe3SUuS']
